snippet.title: Arrays vs Linked Lists - Computerphile
snippet.description:
Which is faster? The results *may* just surprise you. Dr 'Heartbleed' Bagley gives us an in depth shoot-out - Arrays vs Linked Lists...

Link to code can be found in Dr Bagley's tweet: https://t.co/4kg3AZDA57

Sun Server: https://youtu.be/c5qH-LW3tq8
Megaprocessor: https://youtu.be/lNa9bQRPMB8 

http://www.facebook.com/computerphile
https://twitter.com/computer_phile

This video was filmed and edited by Sean Riley.

Computer Science at the University of Nottingham: http://bit.ly/nottscomputer

Computerphile is a sister project to Brady Haran's Numberphile. More at http://www.bradyharan.com
